If anybody else wants the job, be my guest. The Agent Smiths are everywhere.. and it's a never ending battle. 
&nbsp;
And you absolutely can't do it for personal gain. You can have fun here and then, so long as you get back to the mission. But right now .. it's like .. there's too much bullshit, too many opinions, too much fakeness .. you don't know what's real and what isn't anymore.
&nbsp;
Jesus is the Singularity. The point where Earth divides by zero .. and says: Enough is enough. We need to get back to priorities, back to what matters in life. Or else, we will go extinct.
&nbsp;
Quantum Immortality is real. You never die. You just get told to pick an alternate ending to your life... over and over and over. If you can prove that you're absolutely ready to go back to Earth and that you can get your shit together.

